  <h1>End-to-end data &amp; control flow</h1>

  <p>The bot is structured as a small set of long-lived processes (the trading <code>daemon</code>, the <code>lab</code>, the <code>dashboard</code>, and a <code>supervisor</code>) sharing a SQLite state database, an append-only DecisionStore, and a single Alpaca paper account. Every workflow flows through the same orchestrator and risk envelope.</p>

